metadata.description: Collects Star Wars (2013) #1-6, Star Wars: FCBD 2013 #1.  This is Star Wars as you remember it... and as you have never seen it before! We're taking you back to those heady, adventure-filled days following the destruction of the Death Star—when the Empire ruled, the Rebels were on the run, and the galaxy was a dangerous place where anything might happen!
metadata.name: Star Wars: The Rebellion
